content: I am a resident of Haebangchon. It is my favorite place in Korea with a lot of personal thoughts. Always a relaxing alley somewhere, a bar that is so good to have a drink full of comfortable sensibility, HBC is love ❤️
It's a good place to take a walk in Itaewon~ It's difficult to park, so it's better to use public transportation. The night view is beautiful in the evening.
Quiet atmosphere exotic alley clean restaurant is a must-visit street
Be sure to visit Villa de Blue in Haebangchon 🩵🩵 The food is very delicious and the atmosphere is good 😀
The exotic shop in Haebangchon and the road to see Namsan Tower! I think it's good to walk and play
There are a lot of tastes in Haebangchon ㅇㅆ butterbook donuts are really the best
A strangely charming neighborhood liberation village.
This is a restaurant in Haebangchon!! It's like a foreign country and it's fun

It's a great place to take a walk in the city center. The promenade is very well formed. There is also a coffee shop at the entrance, which is a good place to buy a coffee and take a walk.
